<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_titleIndef], is calling from nearby. [asker_pronoun] has deserted the army of [asker_factionName] and is being hunted by (*Threat)a loyalty squad(/Threat). [asker_pronoun] wishes to join you at [map_definite].\n\n[asker_nameDef] knows the location of key outpost containing everything needed to develop psychic powers:\n\n[sitePart1_itemStashContents]\n\nBeware - If you accept [asker_nameDef], you will become an enemy of [asker_factionName]! The pursuing loyalty squad will attack immediately. It is composed of: \n\n[raid/raidPawnKinds]\n\nOnly accept if you wish to fight against [asker_factionName] and develop your psycasters on your own. You will have one year to attack the outpost before it is moved.</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Deserter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_titleIndef]の[asker_nameFull]が付近から通信を送ってきました。 [asker_pronoun]は[asker_factionName]の軍隊から脱走したため(*Threat)忠誠隊(/Threat)に追われています。[asker_pronoun]は[map_definite]に加わりたいと言っています。\n\n[asker_nameDef]は、超能力を身につけるために必要なものが全て揃っている前哨基地の場所を知っています:\n\n[sitePart1_itemStashContents]\n\n注意：[asker_nameDef]を受け入れると、[asker_factionName]の敵となります！忠誠隊はすぐに攻撃してくるでしょう。 構成は以下の通りです: \n\n[raid/raidPawnKinds]\n\n[asker_factionName]と戦いたい場合や、独力で超能力を使えるようになりたい場合のみ受け入れるべきです。前哨基地が消滅するまで一年の攻撃猶予があります。</li>
  </Intro_Deserter.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questName->The Deserter</li>
  -->
  <Intro_Deserter.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questName->脱走兵</li>
  </Intro_Deserter.questNameRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN: {BASETEXT}\n\nBecause you accepted [asker_nameDef], [asker_factionName] has become hostile.\n\nThe loyalty squad that is hunting [asker_objective] will arrive soon. -->
  <Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelAskerBecameHostile.slateRef>{BASETEXT}\n\n[asker_nameDef]を受け入れたため、[asker_factionName]と敵対状態になりました。\n\n[asker_objective]を追跡中の忠誠隊はすぐにやってきます。</Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelAskerBecameHostile.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {BASELABEL}: Loyalty squad -->
  <Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelLoyaltySquad.value.slateRef>{BASELABEL}:忠誠隊</Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelLoyaltySquad.value.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {BASETEXT}\n\nThis is the loyalty squad that was hunting [../asker_nameFull].\n               -->
  <Intro_Deserter.LetterTextLoyaltySquad.value.slateRef>{BASETEXT}\n\n[../asker_nameFull]を追跡中の忠誠隊です。\n              </Intro_Deserter.LetterTextLoyaltySquad.value.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: Quest expired: [resolvedQuestName] -->
  <Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>クエスト期限切れ: [resolvedQuestName]</Intro_Deserter.LetterLabelQuestExpired.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: The key imperial outpost, containing items needed for secret psychic powers, has packed up and moved on. -->
  <Intro_Deserter.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>秘密の超能力の開発に必要なアイテムを含む物資をまとめて、帝国の重要な前哨基地は移動しました。</Intro_Deserter.LetterTextQuestExpired.slateRef>
  
